# Component Rules for React Vite Starter

## Component Structure

1. Use functional components
2. Use TypeScript for type safety
3. Use proper prop types
4. Use proper state management
5. Use proper error handling

## Component Organization

1. Organize components by feature
2. Keep components small and focused
3. Use proper file naming
4. Use proper folder structure
5. Use proper imports

## Component Styling

1. Use CSS modules
2. Use proper class names
3. Use proper CSS organization
4. Use proper CSS variables
5. Use proper CSS best practices

## Component Testing

1. Write unit tests
2. Write integration tests
3. Write end-to-end tests
4. Use proper test organization
5. Use proper test naming

## Component Documentation

1. Use proper JSDoc comments
2. Use proper README files
3. Use proper examples
4. Use proper documentation
5. Use proper documentation best practices
